.el .IP "\-\fBe\fR \f(CWExpires\fR | \-\-\fBexpires\fR \f(CWExpires\fR" 4
.IX Item "-e Expires | --expires Expires"
Set the article header field Expires: to the given value.
.ie n .IP "\-\fBf\fR ""From""\fR | \-\-\fBfrom\fR \f(CW""From""" 4
