Set the article header field Organization: to the given value.
.ie n .IP "\-\fBp\fR ""port""\fR | \-\-\fBport\fR \f(CW""port""" 4
.el .IP "\-\fBp\fR \f(CWport\fR | \-\-\fBport\fR \f(CWport\fR" 4
