.ie n .IP "\-\fBx\fR ""Path""\fR | \-\-\fBpath\fR \f(CW""Path""" 4
.el .IP "\-\fBx\fR \f(CWPath\fR | \-\-\fBpath\fR \f(CWPath\fR" 4
.IX Item "-x Path | --path Path"
Set the article header field Path: to the given value.
